    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《平寇志：邪马台之影》是《平寇志》的付费DLC。</h2>封海平离开了复岭岛，与凉枫凉玉一起踏上了返乡之路。不料在海上遭遇了一起风暴...船只被毁，封海平从岸边醒来之后发现凉枫凉玉都已不见踪影，而通过岸边石碑发现，这里竟然是魏晋时期就有过记载的邪马台国...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/a8b559f804aa6c5a1bb6f593a36a527f.poster.avif?t=1726030058\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/a8b559f804aa6c5a1bb6f593a36a527f.webm?t=1726030058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/a8b559f804aa6c5a1bb6f593a36a527f.mp4?t=1726030058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新模式</h2>Roguelike全新玩法，面对新的敌人，玩家需要先通过三个妖怪的领域，每次进入关卡会随机组合变化，并刷出一些强有力的饰品，将饰品组合携带，获得强大的增益buff，通关将变得更加容易。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/cabcebfab077b2f569a8a55eb6076bc1.poster.avif?t=1726030058\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/cabcebfab077b2f569a8a55eb6076bc1.webm?t=1726030058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/cabcebfab077b2f569a8a55eb6076bc1.mp4?t=1726030058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新地图</h2>探索充满神秘的邪马台，新增5种不同氛围的领域地图供玩家挑战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新敌人</h2>新增5个Boss<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/87cb63322d9c95e68474d1e09de92659.poster.avif?t=1726030058\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/87cb63322d9c95e68474d1e09de92659.webm?t=1726030058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090520/extras/87cb63322d9c95e68474d1e09de92659.mp4?t=1726030058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新装备</h2>新增5套盔甲，可在击败相应Boss后获得，新增老盔甲的新属性，可在商店购买对应强化版本。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新技能</h2>新增副武器技能若干，可在以往的Boss幻象挑战中获得。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >商店功能</h2>在Roguelike关卡中获得的铜钱，可以在商店里用来购买强力装备和武器。",
